"up of :ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>` format flags combined together. For "
"example, a mesh containing both vertices and normals would return a "
"format of ``3`` because :ref:`ArrayMesh.ARRAY_FORMAT_VERTEX "
"<class_ArrayMesh_constant_ARRAY_FORMAT_VERTEX>` is ``1`` and "
":ref:`ArrayMesh.ARRAY_FORMAT_NORMAL "
